        "subject": "LU-4416 osd-ldiskfs: hold i_mutex for truncate in osd_punch",
        "message": "LU-4416 osd-ldiskfs: hold i_mutex for truncate in osd_punch\n\nStarting with 3.10, ext4 started enforcing the expectation that\next4_truncate be called with i_mutex held. This patch adds the\nmutex to the osd_punch so it's properly held.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: If067d0a8d4aca54fcf0b71244b959b2dd4210f5c\n"
      },
